snippet.title: Kirby's Dream Buffet - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Hungry for some 4-player Kirby fun? Race through delicious obstacle courses, collect the most strawberries, and thwart your competition using familiar abilities.

Get ready, Kirby’s Dream Buffet launches exclusively in Nintendo eShop this summer! #Kirby 

https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/kirbys-dream-buffet-switch/

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
